<p><b><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font color="#000000"><font size=-1>"Terry
Green... certainly one of Canada's finest writers"</font></font></font></b>
<br><b><i><font face="Times New Roman,Times"><font color="#CC0000"><font size=-1>&nbsp;</font>Charles
