<center><b><i><font color="#009900"><font size=+2>St. Patrick's Bed</font></font></i></b>
<p><img SRC="stpatscoversmall.jpg" height=250 width=167>
<p>the long-awaited sequel to <b><i>Shadow of Ashland</i></b>,&nbsp;
<br>published by <b>Forge Books</b> <font size=-1>(Tom Doherty Associates,
NY)</font>,
<br>.
<br><font size=-1>(Canadian Distributor: H.B. Fenn &amp; Co. Ltd.)</font>
<p><font size=-2>hardcover, 1st edition (2001) ISBN 0-765-30043-5:</font>
<br><font size=-2>$US21.95</font>
<br><font size=-2>$Cdn31.95</font>
<p><font size=-2>trade paperback (2002)&nbsp; ISBN 0-765-30044-3:</font>
<br><font size=-2>$US12.95</font>
<br><font size=-2>$Cdn17.95</font>
