<hr WIDTH="100%"></center>
<b><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size=-1><a href="StPatsGlobe.html">The
Globe and Mail:</a> </font></font></b><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size=-1>"(a)
modern ghost story...&nbsp;</font></font>
<br><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size=-1>Green expertly commingles
the mythical past with the hard truths of the present in Leo Nolan's aspiration
to be a good father and a good son in this heartfelt novel... It takes
a special writer to delineate the complexities of blood kinship while maintaining
the reader's sympathy for each character."</font></font>
<p><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size=-1><b><a href="http://www.sfsite.com/fsf/2002/cdl0205.htm">Charles
